title: The Great Pottery Throw Down S01E03 PDTV.x264-JIVE.mp4
description:
The Great Pottery Throw Down - Series 1, Episode 3




The potters must make ten identical long-necked vases using the raku technique. This Japanese method of decorating and firing dates back to the 16th century and requires the potters to take their red-hot vases straight out of the kiln and plunge them into a bin full of combustible materials.




Original Air Date: 17-Nov-2015
